name: Admiral Chiraneau
Lore: 'Deep space transmissions expert. Piett''s personal advisor. TIE ace promoted upon Piett''s request.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting a Star Destroyer at a battleground system, adds 1 to your Force drains here and at each other battleground system controlled by a Star Destroyer within 2 parsecs of Chiraneau.',
